OL,5, A former Royal Navy weapons officer who
OL,6, was removed from a submarine because he
OL,7, opposed nuclear weapons is suing the   
OL,8, Ministry of Defence for religious      
OL,9, discrimination.                        
OL,11,FSub Lt Antonio Jardim, a Christian with
OL,12,Fjoint British-Portuguese nationality,  
OL,13,Fwas assigned to HMS Vanguard.          
OL,15,FHe was given the nickname "Trigger"    
OL,16,Fbecause of his "reluctance to pull the 
OL,17,Ftrigger", according to tribunal papers.
OL,19,FMr Jardim was later moved to an onshore
OL,20,Frole in Portsmouth.                    
